Package: package
Type: Package
Title: Create packages from R-code directly
Version: 0.1-0
Date: 08-11-2019
Author: Stefan Böhringer <r-packages@s-boehringer.org>
Maintainer: Stefan Böhringer <r-packages@s-boehringer.org>
Description: This package simplifies package generation by automating the use of `devtools` and `roxygen`. It also makes the development workflow more efficient by allowing ad-hoc development of packages.
License: LGPL
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: 
    roxygen2,
    devtools
Collate: 
    Rpackage.R
Suggests: 
    jsonlite,
    yaml
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
